article.headline: Keishon Porter, Perry Smith Jr. lead North Carolina Central over Carolina University 91-35
article.description: — Keishon Porter and Perry Smith Jr. scored 15 points apiece as North Carolina Central beat Carolina University 91-36 on Monday night.
article.linkText: Keishon Porter, Perry Smith Jr. lead North Carolina Central over Carolina University 91-35
article.story: DURHAM, N.C. -- — Keishon Porter and Perry Smith Jr. scored 15 points apiece as North Carolina Central beat Carolina University 91-36 on Monday night. Porter also contributed four steals for the Eagles (2-6). Smith finished 7 of 12 from the floor. Po'Boigh King had 14 points. The Bruins were led by Jayden Jackson with 13 points. Chris High added 10 points and two steals. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
